query:
UPDATE play_to_artists_extended
                    SET artist_id = $1, artist_name = $2
                    WHERE artist_id = $3
                    AND NOT EXISTS (
                        SELECT 1 FROM play_to_artists_extended existing
                        WHERE existing.play_uri = play_to_artists_extended.play_uri
                        AND existing.artist_id = $1
                    )
